data.description: Short Sale. SHORT SALE - Priced to Move    Affordable Handy Man Special in Fort Myers Shores.  Great location with 4 bedrooms and many updates.  New roof in 2017, with an industrial farmhouse vibe.  Built in bench seating in the dining area and wood feature wall in the living area.  Wood laminate flooring throughout.  Spacious back yard with room for a pool.  City water & sewer.    Please forward all offers with proof of funds to the listing email
